    "title": "京东开放平台恶意倒卖细则",
    "followRuleId": "3407",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1 </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">恶意倒卖：商家在事前未取得消费者授权的情况下，以购买他人店铺内商品完成自己店铺内交易，或搬运他人店铺内的商品，严重干扰市场正常运营秩序，使商品品质、售后服务、价格公平等消费者权益无法保障，从而影响买家购物体验的行为。 </span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1 </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东将根据系统识别、媒体报道、用户投诉及商家举报等多维度对违规店铺进行判定，当识别到商家店铺涉嫌恶意倒卖时，将根据违规情形对商家或同时对其关联店铺进行预警及开具违约单。此外，平台将有权依据违规行为具体影响给予商品管理（商品下架、限制发品数量、商品搜索降权等）、限制店铺的部分权限（流量降权/屏蔽、限制提报营销活动、冻结货款、降低店铺星级、限制新开店铺、限制使用第三方平台运单、限制新品标识等）、资金管控包括不限于（加收风险保证金、关联店铺资金管控、扣除店铺资金、延长账期等）、店铺清退等处置。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、为什么对恶意倒卖进行管控？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">恶意倒卖行为不仅涉嫌侵犯消费者的知情权、个人信息保护权，且影响商品价格、商品质量、服务质量等权益体验，扰乱平台经营秩序。同时可能涉嫌侵犯货源方的知识产权、对货源方构成不正当竞争等法律风险。 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、违规严重程度档位说明</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违约金划分为七个档位（M1-M7），具体金额标准如下：</span></p>\n<table style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-all; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 75pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 130.5pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"174\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 399.75pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"533\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金标准</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 130.5pt;\" width=\"174\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害一级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 399.75pt;\" width=\"533\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">50</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元及以下</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 130.5pt;\" width=\"174\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害二级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 399.75pt;\" width=\"533\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">固定金额 200元/500元/800元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 130.5pt;\" width=\"174\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害三级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 399.75pt;\" width=\"533\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">「违规商品/商家/门店」近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 130.5pt;\" width=\"174\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害四级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 399.75pt;\" width=\"533\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">「违规商品/商家/门店」近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\